title: Bug 116609[Regression] Orange color not working
description: Bug 116609[Regression] Orange color is not working properly. When the color orange is chosen, it is not being displayed correctly.
OB: When selecting the orange color, the preview does not show the expected orange color.
EB: When selecting the orange color, the preview should display the correct shade of orange.
SR:
Steps to reproduce:
1. Open the color selection menu.
2. Choose the color orange.
3. Check the preview area to see if the selected color is displayed correctly.
